{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/-/markdown/blog/2020-01-03-diagrams/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ce1dff60-a47f-5da5-b022-8ef2b84ce479","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2020-01-03-diagrams/"},"frontmatter":{"category":"docs","tags":["website","markdown","mermaid","graphviz"],"title":"Demonstrating diagrams","date":"2020-01-03T00:00:00.000Z"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","id":"71357d4a-5b23-53f5-aab4-492d0864e9d7","modifiedTime":"2020-02-27T15:31:11.627Z","birthTime":"2020-02-27T15:31:11.627Z"},"html":"<p>You can put mermaidjs and graphviz diagrams in your markdown!</p>\n<p>Code like:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token code\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">```</span><span class=\"token code-language\">dot</span>\n<span class=\"token code-block language-dot\">graph {\n    a -- b;\n    b -- c;\n    a -- c;\n    d -- c;\n    e -- c;\n    e -- a;\n}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">```</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>(you can use three backticks or three ~s - either works - I'm using both to make this page work!)</p>\n<p>Results in:</p>\n<svg width=\"199pt\" height=\"260pt\" viewBox=\"0.00 0.00 199.00 260.00\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\">\n<g id=\"graph0\" class=\"graph\" transform=\"scale(1 1) rotate(0) translate(4 256)\">\n<title>%0</title>\n<polygon fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"transparent\" points=\"-4,4 -4,-256 195,-256 195,4 -4,4\"/>\n<!-- a -->\n<g id=\"node1\" class=\"node\">\n<title>a</title>\n<ellipse fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" cx=\"137\" cy=\"-162\" rx=\"27\" ry=\"18\"/>\n<text text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"137\" y=\"-157.8\" font-family=\"Times,serif\" font-size=\"14.00\" fill=\"#000000\">a</text>\n</g>\n<!-- b -->\n<g id=\"node2\" class=\"node\">\n<title>b</title>\n<ellipse fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" cx=\"99\" cy=\"-90\" rx=\"27\" ry=\"18\"/>\n<text text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"99\" y=\"-85.8\" font-family=\"Times,serif\" font-size=\"14.00\" fill=\"#000000\">b</text>\n</g>\n<!-- a&#45;&#45;b -->\n<g id=\"edge1\" class=\"edge\">\n<title>a--b</title>\n<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" d=\"M127.9945,-144.937C122.0248,-133.626 114.2149,-118.8282 108.2048,-107.4407\"/>\n</g>\n<!-- c -->\n<g id=\"node3\" class=\"node\">\n<title>c</title>\n<ellipse fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" cx=\"126\" cy=\"-18\" rx=\"27\" ry=\"18\"/>\n<text text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"126\" y=\"-13.8\" font-family=\"Times,serif\" font-size=\"14.00\" fill=\"#000000\">c</text>\n</g>\n<!-- a&#45;&#45;c -->\n<g id=\"edge3\" class=\"edge\">\n<title>a--c</title>\n<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" d=\"M137.3574,-143.6842C137.5331,-125.4671 137.3246,-96.7409 135,-72 133.862,-59.8878 131.612,-46.3878 129.6465,-35.9159\"/>\n</g>\n<!-- b&#45;&#45;c -->\n<g id=\"edge2\" class=\"edge\">\n<title>b--c</title>\n<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" d=\"M105.6742,-72.2022C109.8593,-61.0419 115.2321,-46.7143 119.4026,-35.593\"/>\n</g>\n<!-- d -->\n<g id=\"node4\" class=\"node\">\n<title>d</title>\n<ellipse fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" cx=\"27\" cy=\"-90\" rx=\"27\" ry=\"18\"/>\n<text text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"27\" y=\"-85.8\" font-family=\"Times,serif\" font-size=\"14.00\" fill=\"#000000\">d</text>\n</g>\n<!-- d&#45;&#45;c -->\n<g id=\"edge4\" class=\"edge\">\n<title>d--c</title>\n<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" d=\"M45.6211,-76.4574C63.3208,-63.5849 89.7904,-44.3343 107.4624,-31.4819\"/>\n</g>\n<!-- e -->\n<g id=\"node5\" class=\"node\">\n<title>e</title>\n<ellipse fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" cx=\"164\" cy=\"-234\" rx=\"27\" ry=\"18\"/>\n<text text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"164\" y=\"-229.8\" font-family=\"Times,serif\" font-size=\"14.00\" fill=\"#000000\">e</text>\n</g>\n<!-- e&#45;&#45;a -->\n<g id=\"edge6\" class=\"edge\">\n<title>e--a</title>\n<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" d=\"M157.3258,-216.2022C153.1407,-205.0419 147.7679,-190.7143 143.5974,-179.593\"/>\n</g>\n<!-- e&#45;&#45;c -->\n<g id=\"edge5\" class=\"edge\">\n<title>e--c</title>\n<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" d=\"M167.7474,-216.0931C169.7466,-205.6241 171.9966,-192.1241 173,-180 177.0478,-131.0908 167.4587,-117.866 150,-72 145.2554,-59.5355 139.1406,-45.8051 134.2707,-35.3087\"/>\n</g>\n</g>\n</svg>\n<p>Similarly for mermaid.js (a JavaScript tool a bit like Plantuml):</p>\n<div class=\"mermaid\">graph TD\nA[Hard] -->|Text| B(Round)\nB --> C{Decision}\nC -->|One| D[Result 1]\nC -->|Two| E[Result 2]</div>\n<div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\nAlice->>John: Hello John, how are you?\nloop Healthcheck\n    John->>John: Fight against hypochondria\nend\nNote right of John: Rational thoughts!\nJohn-->>Alice: Great!\nJohn->>Bob: How about you?\nBob-->>John: Jolly good!</div>","tableOfContents":""},"asciidoc":null},"pageContext":{"kind":"markdown","slug":"/blog/2020-01-03-diagrams/","title":"Demonstrating diagrams","tags":["website","markdown","mermaid","graphviz"],"category":"docs","date":"2020-01-03T00:00:00.000Z","selectedTag":"markdown","selectedCategory":null}}}